{"type": "article", "id": 48261, "title": "家用灭火器也得有设计感，这款就不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-14T23:30:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 26212, "name": "Studio Lorier"}, {"id": 44178, "name": "MOO"}, {"id": 46325, "name": "Sturlesidesign"}, {"id": 46326, "name": "Build With Hubs"}, {"id": 46327, "name": "Lia"}, {"id": 46328, "name": "Wooseok Kim"}, {"id": 46329, "name": "Timothy Goodman"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 121, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171214220532lEmLYJayrRFTqXAv.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>\"World's First\" Flushable Pregnancy Test by Lia</h3><p>美国初创公司 Lia 开发了一种由可持续生物降解材料制成的可冲洗妊娠测试方案。Lia 是个全是女性组成的设计团队，他们想为女性提供一种更带有私密性人性关怀的测试怀孕方法。</p><p>它由无纺天然植物纤维制成，类似于卫生棉的制造材料。与传统的妊娠测试相同，用户使用该试剂盒，两行显示阳性结果，一行显示阴性结果。测试准确率达 99%。按照 Lia 团队的说法，这将是世界上“第一个也是唯一一个可冲洗、可生物降解的妊娠测试产品”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214220624cJtPWdqv1XTpkHQ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214220624WsmY14oqt8NXZJKh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.218697\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214220625FrEVUZKD0OnkupvR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.222927\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/12/13/lia-launches-worlds-first-flushable-pregnancy-test-design-products/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>2v Geodesic Dome Kit by Build With Hubs</h3><p>英国公司 Build With Hubs 开发了一套网格状球顶套装工具包，其最大特点在于可以快速方便地搭建起来，套装内包含了所需的全部工具。不管你是为孩子们搭建一个小型游乐区、野餐地还是任何需要它的场合，都可以短时间内实现，拆卸也极为方便，且便于携带。售价 114 英镑，<a href=\"https://shop.buildwithhubs.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221212js8elZvzg7UbFYd1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142212121hKzacgmSQ7HZXEG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221213wAlmDV5QFcu39yfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142212138HE05rqGoakCYWO2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Dragonfly Wall Lamp by Sturlesidesign</h3><p>以色列设计工作室 SturlesiDesign，在灯具设计上颇有想法。他们最新推出的壁灯，没点亮时看起来就是一根平淡无奇的小棍子，点亮后，可以在墙壁上投射出蜻蜓的翅膀，和灯的主体组合成了一只金色翅膀的蜻蜓。一下就让了无生趣的墙壁活了起来。壁灯的主体采用了铜作为主要材质，凸显出了灯具的品质感。经过抛光处理的铜管配上经过花纹处理的亚克力共同组成蜻蜓的外形。售价 95 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/dragonfly-wall-lamp-sturlesidesign-03-28-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221253hqswOGoHetxBlV3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142212535IThJrvz4FWPONlC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221253DGAbU2OJhwNzFEog.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.764000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221253dTiz6NVheAwSgU2p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142212542NVTdz6cKuBbvWeM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.764000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Statement Notebook by MOO and Timothy Goodman</h3><p>工作中难免遇到枯燥冗长的会议，MOO 和纽约设计师兼插画师 Timothy Goodman 为了解决这个问题，推出了一款名为“Meetings Kill Creativity”的笔记本，希望这款色彩鲜明充满活力的工具，能够激发人们的创造力，同时实现高质量输出。</p><p>设计师称：“我们非常喜欢这次作品所用的反讽方式，人们用着我的限量版笔记本开着无聊的会议，我希望能够提醒它们开会时间要尽量短，希望能够让我们的生活中少一些会议多一些创造力。”笔记本沿用了 Timothy Goodman 一贯的作画风格，采用了他独有的励志语录、原创插画，在中心页甚至还采用了整个页面的插图。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221413m8jd3ahCgAtzElL5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142214134vJMesVrTuWK8Dto.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221414wtdKSf6Iki1CyJb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142214148a2jP9Ro4et0QdSI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221414hBN2EiDfWjQ8q3xJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.953545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221414qtAwRSExp1VHuonv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.051345\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BLEND by Wooseok Kim</h3><p>你对灭火器的第一印象是什么？笨重的红色喷瓶？总之，那是一个和家居环境极不协调的家伙，你肯定不愿意将它放在家中能够看见的位置。</p><p>韩国设计师 Wooseok Kim 想要改变这一现状，他设计了一款名为 BLEND 的灭火器，外壳采用半透明的聚碳酸酯制成，内置烟雾检测传感器，当传感器发现有烟雾，不仅会自动报警，底部 LED 灯也会点亮，提示你灭火器放在哪里。它的外形小巧，简约，重点是不会让你觉得和家居环境产生审美冲突。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221440nW2xZdomye4wJP3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221440vp6BP7EOZnTsDbcC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142214410aF3Ne6gZqLyhXzG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.874286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221441cWZ8NRxdiPY3kXQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221441gVzc1r8xt6PTGpsB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.141905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221441TL4DflRWOsIypQq6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2017/12/13/an-exquisite-extinguisher-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hybrid Chair by Studio Lorier</h3><p>设计师 Sander Lorier 在鹿特丹有一间小小的公寓，他希望拥有一张舒服的沙发椅，于是把沙发椅和餐椅合二为一，设计了一把名为 Hybrid 的椅子，运用的原理非常简单，以额外的木板连接座位和椅背，再在座位底部安置一条连接椅背的绳子，绳子松开时座位向下垂，变成沙发椅，把绳子向上拉便把座位提起，成为餐椅。</p><p>虽然没有复杂的技术，却示范了如何有创意地将简单的小技巧运用于设计，轻松解决问题。售价 745 至 875 欧元不等，<a href=\"https://studiolorier.com/product/hybrid-chair/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=f0519q7znjx&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221632CsDHxiUcfK1pmzNW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221633MvbzwxtI4FOXd9Ki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712142216339pPoI75wOjnZKV14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221633VA3w4IaF0nPDktX1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171214221632J8x4Oeo3dKBi75l9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}